《'''興盛'''》（{{lang-en|''Thrive: What on Earth Will It Take?''}}）是一部2011年[[美國|美國]][[紀錄片|紀錄片]]，由史蒂夫·蓋聶（Steve Gagné）和金伯利·卡特·甘布爾（Kimberly Carter-Gamble）執導。紀錄片由[[福斯特·甘布爾|福斯特·甘布爾]]講述。片中談及的主題包括菁英意圖控制全球的[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]、[[環面|環面]]、[[免費能源被打壓陰謀論|自由能源]]和[[麥田圈|麥田圈]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=Scions and Wonders: Has a Procter and Gamble Heir Discovered the Key to Universal Energy?|url=http://betabeat.com/2012/09/scions-and-wonders-has-a-proctor-and-gamble-heir-discovered-the-key-to-universal-energy/|accessdate=2021-01-23|publisher=New York Observer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120928015430/http://betabeat.com/2012/09/scions-and-wonders-has-a-proctor-and-gamble-heir-discovered-the-key-to-universal-energy/|archivedate=2012-09-28|date=2012-09-26}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Ready to Thrive|url=https://goodtimes.sc/santa-cruz-arts-entertainment/film/thrive-movie-review/|accessdate=2021-01-24|date=2012-03-07|last=Archer|first=Greg|work=Good Times Santa Cruz|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=New Age of Paranoia|url=https://www.sfreporter.com/movies/2012/04/17/new-age-of-paranoia/|newspaper=Santa Fe Reporter|accessdate=2021-01-24|language=en-US|date=2012-04-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The THRIVE Documentary: What On Earth Will It Take? (To Change It)|url=https://www.collective-evolution.com/2016/09/09/the-thrive-documentary-what-on-earth-will-it-take-to-change-it/|accessdate=2021-01-24|date=2016-09-09|last=Walia|first=Arjun|publisher=Collective Evolution|language=en-US}}</ref>2011年11月11日，在[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]首映<ref name=":1" />。

《興盛》被翻譯為19種語言，在網路上累積了超過七百萬的觀看次數<ref name=":0" />。

2020年9月26日，續集《興盛2》上映<ref>{{Cite web|title=Groundbreaking Documentary Showcases Solutions To Make The World Truly Thrive|url=https://www.collective-evolution.com/2020/09/02/groundbreaking-documentary-showcases-solutions-to-make-the-world-truly-thrive/|accessdate=2021-01-24|date=2020-09-02|last=Martino|first=Joe|publisher=Collective Evolution|language=en-US}}</ref>。

